# PURPOSE:
#   Download and merge all required NHANES 2015-2020 modules needed for
#   the BioClockR biological age pipeline. Uses the nhanesA R package
#   for automated SAS Transport (.XPT) file retrieval.
#
# DATA SOURCE:
#   CDC NHANES 2015-2016 + 2017-March 2020 pre-pandemic cycles.
